 is proportional to the fraction 1 over lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"B is proportional to the fraction 1 over lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>B</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>r</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B is proportional to the fraction 1 over lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"B is proportional to the fraction 1 over lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>B</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>r</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B is proportional to lowercase r\"><math alttext=\"B is proportional to lowercase r\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>B</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi>r</mi></math></span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR802603_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">A</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">B</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">C</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">D</p>"],"answer":2}]